{"tid":617621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣鬧市 南亞裔男童高處墮下送院搶救","createTime":"2018-04-05T06:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T06:15:32.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"63e02a824f1ddc96155518d1fae6ba3c87f58012","tid":617621,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:15:32.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣鬧市 男童高處墮下送院搶救<br />\n<br />\n灣仔登龍街49號金龍大廈，中午1時10分，有途人報警指一名年約4-5歲南亞裔男童，倒卧大廈1樓簷篷，懷疑他由上址4樓單位墮下，男童被發現時仍清醒，警員及救護員接報到場，將男童救起，男童由父親抱著送院搶救，警方正了解其墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180405/58036614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F58036614&d=8%2BmwyUVWATMUob%2FDox0LjsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e662af92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F58036614&h=f331150b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180405/58036614</a>"}]}